628
01:14:25,984 --> 01:14:27,569
Moj si.

629
01:14:28,613 --> 01:14:31,741
Spremni, kreći!

630
01:14:37,330 --> 01:14:39,416
Ne dopusti da probije, Oher.

631
01:14:42,043 --> 01:14:46,214
Cijelu noć, debeli.
Imam te.

632
01:14:49,677 --> 01:14:53,722
To je moj dečko.
-U redu je!

633
01:15:00,146 --> 01:15:01,605
Druga runda.

634
01:15:08,153 --> 01:15:09,530
Mijenjaj se.

635
01:15:18,498 --> 01:15:22,335
Oher, ne dopusti da uđu iznutra.
Koristi glavu.

636
01:15:22,628 --> 01:15:24,547
Što Bart radi? Ništa.

637
01:15:29,177 --> 01:15:31,971
Još nismo završili, cijelu utakmicu.

638
01:15:38,145 --> 01:15:39,354
Dodaj!

639
01:15:46,736 --> 01:15:48,655
Zašto još jedno dodavanje?

640
01:15:50,198 --> 01:15:56,621
